:
"Search and browse books on Project Gutenberg. For information about Project Gutenberg, please visit https://www.gutenberg.org/"
,
"cn"
:
"搜索和浏览 Project Gutenberg 中的书籍. 关于 Project Gutenberg，请访问 https://www.gutenberg.org/"
}
,
"#keyword"
:
[
"Project Gutenberg books"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x gtb"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有可用的书籍"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all available books"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gtb search Dumas"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 搜索 Dumas 相关的书籍"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Search for books by Dumas"
}
,
{
